# Commit the shared project skill tree (Claude Code's documented location).
# The rest of the developer-local root .claude/ stays ignored. Anchored to the
# repo root so the nested example-pack .claude/ rules above are untouched.
!/.claude/
/.claude/*
!/.claude/skills/

# sync-project-agents writes local migration backups here; don't commit them.
.agents/migration/
.gc/

# Dolt database files (added by bd init)
.dolt/
*.db

# Pipeline artifacts
.decompose/
reports/

# Beads / Dolt files (added by bd init)
